text: Wisches is a commune. It is in Grand Est in the Bas-Rhin department in northeast France. == Notable places == Some notable places around Wisches are: * Le Struthof at 8 km (direction south) Le Struthof is the only Nazi Concentration camp to have been built in France. * Mont-Sainte-Odile at 13 km (direction east-south-east). * Rosheim at 15 km (direction east). * Chateau d'Andlau Castle at 16 km (direction south-east).
